@startuml
actor User
participant "Web App" as Web
participant "API Gateway" as API
database "User DB" as DB

User -> Web: Login
Web -> API: POST /auth
API -> DB: Validate credentials
DB --> API: User data
API --> Web: JWT token
Web --> User: Welcome

note right of User
User authenticated
end note
note over API, DB
Secure connection
end note
@enduml
